Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這呢 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕登場！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 十字陣形 就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,655)\fs30}cross dog
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows 歸航剛瑠島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows呼叫CDC 運輸機移交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(795,655)\fs30}Track hand over
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫Arrows 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cetus由CDC繼續引導
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫CDC 請批准Mk.Ⅶ出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將Mk.Ⅶ移至剛瑠島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅸ 上前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 準備迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,655)\fs30}scepter ready
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請準備進行同步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CDC批准了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我們這一代最後的常規駕駛員了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在兩分鐘內開動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要利用就利用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你負責後方支援 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒必要連一騎的工作都攬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…你並沒有明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 Mk.Ⅴ 上前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Nicht？連Mk.Sein都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些被封存的機體要糾纏我們到什麼時候…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕同步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓它們干涉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我存在於此刻的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時隔四年半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一次和駕駛員共享痛覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內部被侵食 無法止痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(785,655)\fs30}Pain block
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強制切斷 左臂壞死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(770,655)\fs30}necrosis
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把敵人逼出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,申請進行飽和攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後撤到防線08 動作快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:08:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光學 熱力 電波 電子 音波探測 無反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 迴轉體的氣壓發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅶ 捕捉目標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 開始迎擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,655)\fs30}scepter go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花招不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據所羅門的分析 敵人的內核只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其餘的都是虛像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虛像？可是它們能攻擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 互相掩護啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是Cetus 我們也參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起擊退威脅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍 三部法芙娜前往彥島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要共同作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一號機負責上空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二號機掩護噴火的那部機體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}torch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和揮劍的那部一起作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算可以戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在那樣的高速運動中打中了？好高超的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 來幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部機體是靠頭部進行攻擊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒法和你們相互理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認敵人已消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門系統發出應答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 陣內 我在這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Festum…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼…這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我們放進來了一個相當重要的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎接來訪者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼 收隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那些人不可信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭乘法芙娜的時間越長 就越會被同化現象侵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去體檢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 沒事吧 暉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他們回來就要開總結會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先體檢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是眼睜睜在一旁看著 很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到達D島了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的Mir是空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠接納我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最新機體就這麼報廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你能撿回一條命就算賺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 將陵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看家辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把部隊當什麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還把真矢也拖下水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把指揮工作全丟給陣內 正經點幹活行不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前真是抱歉了 將陵參謀長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人類軍總務部的那雷恩·魏茨曼·玻色上將
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(784,655)}Narain Weizmann Bose
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你們的接納
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是龍宮島Alvis司令官 真壁史彥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在人類軍的部隊是由將校率領的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在光是上將就有一百人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軍銜已經成了擺設
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能由生命和希望尚存的人承擔起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了確保你們不能使用武力 我們要監視法芙娜駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員就是他們三人 還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你開得動？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史上最高齡駕駛員的身份是我小小的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您允許駕駛員之間的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是真壁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 他不是真壁一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 超級王牌駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給了我們真壁因子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是破壞了北極Mir的駕駛員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D島的真壁一騎 是我們的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒怎麼 就是想看看它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經戰鬥得足夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這部Mk.Sein沒人開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它太特別了 別人都開不動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計劃在成功取出內核之後就把它沉到海底
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西想要駕駛員的命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再靠近它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是勸也勸不動 我就跟你來硬的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手 真暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 打擾你了 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥後來瓶這個真是棒透了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明想不當駕駛員了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是一想到下次就得輪到後輩上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又覺得不能不做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟劍司前輩那時也是為了我們而一直堅持開法芙娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮痛劑打多了會成癮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見醫生說如果還是會痛 就和暉一起接受脈衝治療
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 美羽在Alvis嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是要讓她和人類軍見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽 聽說是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見 快穿衣服 穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個羞什麼呢 是不是醫生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是還嫩著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 還不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就行了啦 乖乖等一等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家等好久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就相信你在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定 肯定不是我的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們天各一方時就在互相交流嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是通過Mir的仲介而引發的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說Mir？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Festum的思維中樞 可以化為萬物的萬能結構體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你們對牠應該更為瞭解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女孩也能與Mir交流嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她弟弟似乎在機緣巧合之下得到了Mir的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是倖存下來的北極Mir的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉說是她弟弟教給了她和那塊碎片交流的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的弟弟現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天 她居住的城市變成了戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她弟弟通過Mir的碎片勸導對方停止殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和Festum對話了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她的弟弟和家人則被Mir同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有她一個人活了下來 至今仍不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 像她這樣能夠和Mir交流的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們稱之為「通識者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,655)\fs30}Esperanto
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}註：Esperanto是世界語的名字 而這個詞在世界語中的意思即「希望」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是希望？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 這個詞是人類創造出的人工語言的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為相互理解 消除紛爭而創造的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是真正的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然已經開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商店街那邊都還沒開始營業呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該多休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家體檢完後就會來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝口先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人訂外賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是要開會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了啦 我去就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎…在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陣內先生 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據真壁司令的指示 我們帶客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的指示？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫愛絲維婭·費因 是珀耳修斯中隊的法芙娜駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(391,655)}Aishwarya Fein
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請叫我小愛 真壁一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會知道我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫比利·摩根 是個駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(573,655)}Billy Morgan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是珀耳修斯中隊法芙娜隊隊長 喬納森·光弘·巴特藍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(930,655)}Jonathan Mitsuhiro Bertrand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能見到傳說中的英雄 真是不勝感激
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了你 我才能夠戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 多虧了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厲害了 沒想到真的能見到真壁因子的提供者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(990,655)\fs30}presence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因子？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你將會懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的希望的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不一定意味著和平的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要守護還等同於戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望也就還處在紛爭之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們冒著失去一切的風險尋求著未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的任何道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都沒有餘地選擇
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
